    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, NameTag, AclfMultiStudyCase, MultiStudyCase, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContingencyAnalysisImpl, DStabMultiStudyCaseImpl

    public class AclfMultiStudyCaseImpl
extends MultiStudyCaseImpl
implements AclfMultiStudyCase
    An implementation of the model object 'Aclf Multi Study Case'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Remote Job Creation
    • Lf Tolerance
    • Bus Voltage Upper Limit PU
    • Bus Voltage Lower Limit PU
    • Aclf Grid Option
    • Bus Result Summary
    • Branch Result Summary
